Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The water gets deeper that way, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're looking at? There's a damsel in distress here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi, you perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi, you perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally come back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Heilige Wasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure rising in the mana chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy charging, 120%...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was caught up in a fierce battle last night, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it'd be safer for you not to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eighth-grader syndrome is a real pain to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the monster from Greek mythology and video games?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Last night I was investigating the Ethereal Horizon, when suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to keep it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This beast will serve as my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A chimera from the depths of oblivion should prove invaluable in my search for the Ethereal Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The priestess of the Ethereal Horizon Overseers displays immune hyperreaction to chimeras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean your sister is allergic to cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus I enlist the help of my comrade, the Dark Flame Mas—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A week has passed since I started high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thanks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dark Flame Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over time, I got used to dealing with this serious case of eighth-grader syndrome.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.00,0:04:43.13,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(148,436)\fnOne Off Mincho\b1\fs56\xshad3\yshad3\blur0.5\pos(377.334,268.666)}Priestess... of Melodies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzuha and Yumeha both love animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mom wouldn't object either,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but doing what you want is against my principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, you're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's working in Jakarta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}I must be careful not to let anything slip about my past,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you know that Jakarta is the origin of the Japanese word for "potato"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but at least for now I've managed to blend into my class without any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well then, Hirakata, you're class librarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow ended up as one of the class reps after Isshiki nominated me as a joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but that might not be such a bad thing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeroom's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice job, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough work being a class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Oh, who're you gonna vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to open the poll soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What poll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The cutie poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about it, didn't I? We guys are gonna vote to decide who's the cutest in the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you going with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls won't be impressed if they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, they won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like these, nothing's stronger than the bonds we share as men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you come to the science lab during lunch break?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? The science teacher asked us for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta check the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven, eight, nine, ten... There's twelve of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, twelve it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it for this shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This aroma... is it Asience? Petal Sassoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten used to being a class rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all pretty new to me still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you notice anything, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I tend to forget stuff, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You didn't strike me as absent-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I pay special attention to making sure I don't come across that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a class rep, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You always seem so calm and collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been class rep a bunch of times before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But you got recommended. \NYou must have experience too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've done it once back in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but mostly I preferred not to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first met, I was thinking how alike we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? It was at the station, on the day of the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't even know my class or name then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but when I got to class and saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought "Oh, it's him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down! It's too early to get nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at least her opinion of me isn't bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that if I go down this path,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might actually get a life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do the rest tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I make a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, let's simulate it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Predict her reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong, Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you? Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, my head's spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing some work for the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So many drugs for such a simple school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The arm of the Overseers is long indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you just quit this charade and take off the coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even yours, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, take it off! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How bold... Telling me to undress...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that intentionally, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't play with the chemicals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, the chimera lacks the mana to manifest itself in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I must supplement it by artificial means.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a gray cat with a mark on its forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi picked it up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Takanashi. It's Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A gray cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really Dodomen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:46.31,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\c&H84807F&\fs40\frx6\fry0\blur0.6\fscy120\frz19.92\pos(367,198)}Have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:46.31,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\c&H84807F&\fs40\frz12.07\frx6\fry0\blur0.6\fscy120\pos(433,170)}you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:46.31,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\c&H84807F&\fs40\frz12.07\frx6\fry0\blur0.6\fscy120\pos(501,151)}seen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:46.31,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\c&H84807F&\fs40\frx6\fry0\blur0.6\fscy120\pos(573,136)\frz9.748}this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:46.31,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\c&H84807F&\fs40\frx6\fry0\blur0.6\fscy120\frz4.35\pos(645,125)}cat{\fnyryr uzura\fs30}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:46.31,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.15\fnMarker SD\c&H84807F&\fs26\blur0.6\fscy120\frz11.75\pos(467,288)}Answers to Dodomen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but it pretty much fits this description.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Its behind is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has wings—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my cat's about that big too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean its wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When did she get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,About a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come and see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,May Seventh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.13,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\fs28\blur0.6\c&H84807F&\pos(956.571,333.999)\frz18.63}Contact {\alpha&FF&}Tsuyuri Kumin,\N{\alpha&00&}Class 2-4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.13,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\fs28\blur0.6\c&H84807F&\frz19.63\pos(952.304,321.199)}Tsuyuri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.13,C2-TS,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\fnMarker SD\b1\fs28\blur0.6\c&H84807F&\pos(1027.5,291.932)\frz23.21}Kumin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's pronounced "Tsuyuri".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsuyuri Kumin. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I'm Togashi Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I live on the second floor, \Nand Takanashi lives right above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys must go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, she just moved in recent—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic code unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just open it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It opened... It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must check my room for anomalies in the fabric of spacetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad for trying to barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We girls have our secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Dark Side,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to the twirling world of chaotic chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize you said it twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you like cute plushies, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Black Tortoise of the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a military Mauser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cooler than I thought you ever could be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sacred gun that can exorcise devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can totally see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mauser really is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you know, the original model of this gun was made a century ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's pretty awesome, called the M712, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You love stuff like that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, all objects in this room are\N placed according to the laws of astrology.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving anything is strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, cleaning is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Emit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And where's the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see it? Well, I wouldn't expect normal people to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our senior. Show some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She blended in so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give it a rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is this the right one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Its chin looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose cat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose cat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Airtight blast doors, lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate radiation barriers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel, evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? This isn't even your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be done in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they going to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will overcome this barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Schwarzschild, full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Avalon Sm—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Togashi Yuuta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takanashi Tooka, the sister of this freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We should talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still going on about her \N"Wicked Eye" or whatever it's called,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,just like when she was back in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that she knows I'm allergic to cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet she takes one in just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't care how much trouble it causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but could you take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That cat. I can't get rid of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you give it to someone or leave it on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,just get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really about whether I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then thanks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a record of what was said on this apartment's balcony two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}This is no charade! No fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}This world shall be conquered by darkness as of the year 2012!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}What's wrong, Yuuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I'm not Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I am the Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I wield the power of the flames of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's your voice, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I can feel the winds of change!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that again! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}What are you talking about? There's no wind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I can feel... I can feel the power overwhelming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Don't shout things like that! People will laugh at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}What care have I for the foolishness of mortals?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I like uploading stuff to video-sharing websites.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Listen, my beloved sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Mom, I'm sorry I didn't respect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi, let's run away together! Let's run to the ends of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold you to those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The ends of the Earth are all around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our world is round, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister was really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We must escape, and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a high-level priestess of the Overseers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not take her powers lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood shall be a sacrifice to these chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloody Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She can even teleport. It's truly frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you just being careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so much fun! Like a horror movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw something sparkle in the distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuyuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put this... I feel like my life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, I have no means to defeat the priestess in this time space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will eventually have to confront her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to go by yourselves. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's live together once this battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop tripping death flags!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, you must run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find the Ethereal Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to call me Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch the chimera, Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth, Schwarz Sechs Prototype Mark II!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rend reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shatter synapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanishment... this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed the call of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I summon thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Königin der Nacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... actually holding her ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nergal Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wicked Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite enough of your delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, keep that cat away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I want for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Use these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That should have ended with my Wicked Twinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It only works that way in your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It still stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can keep a model gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't let you return to your former home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, can I keep a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, a kitty! It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kumin's cat was found unhurt soon after.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.55,0:22:11.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\an8}inside identity ibasho wa doko
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.55,0:22:11.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Inside identity! Where do I belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:11.67,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}inside identity ibasho wa doko
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:11.67,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Inside identity! Where do I belong?
