Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.11,0:22:24.73,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Getting it wrong is a shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:24.73,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}kanchigai ga haji ka douka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:24.73,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Getting it wrong is a shame?
